<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat tuah
 Ka sining vial-te a, min thiang thangthat
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat law
 Ka sualnak vial-te kha, a ka ngaihthiam.

[C1]
   Halleluijah, na min, thiang kan thangthat
   Na min thiang cu, ka ca, damnak a si
   Na tuah mi thil, ruangah, kan in thangthat
   Bawipa na lian-ngannak, kan in thangthat.

[V2]
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat tuah
 Ka zawtnak vial-te kha, a ka damter
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat law
 Thlan chungin a, ka khamh, a dawtnak in.

[V3]
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat tuah
 Ka nunnak cu, thiltha, in a khahter
 Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa, cu thangthat law
 Ka no peng i, Mupi, bangin ka thawng.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>MAW KA NUNNAK BAWIPA CU THANGTHAT TUAH</title>
</song>